no#1CLRBLND: lisbon : june 2021
leica monochrome, 28mm, jpg

[excerpt] these days. when we had nothing but us. a sunny day in spring during covid. coffee and laughter. in quarantine together on a bolkony in alfama.

collector can claim the access to an owners only MONOCHROMIA art space and the full essay and poem to this photography.

minted 3.3.2022 by @dajanaeder on foundation.app as part of the "CLRBLND" collection.
